Webpage description (html):
Introducing Gemstone Enchantment Lights - a dazzling fusion of nature's beauty and modern technology. Perfect for resale, these lights will enchant your customers and their surroundings. 

The lights come with a USB connector for hassle-free power supply. Customers can easily plug them into their computers, power banks, or USB wall chargers. Please note that an adapter is not included as part of the product. 

The length of the lights is 227cm.

Bask in the calming and celestial blue light of Celestite. These lights bring a sense of tranquility and connection with the spiritual realm, making them ideal for meditation spaces or a serene bedroom ambiance.  

Transform any space into a realm of enchantment with Gemstone Enchantment Lights.
